data.description: This open concept floor plan is PERFECT for entertaining or cozy nights at home. The first floor features a study, an electric fireplace and granite counters in the kitchen.  All Bedrooms & bonus/flex space are located on the 2nd floor. The backyard is an entertainer's dream- completed with a firepit and a pergola. This gorgeous home is situated on large level lot in lovely neighborhood just minutes from I-295. This location provides easy access to Ft. Liberty and Fayetteville while still offering a rural, country setting. USDA Eligible and SOLAR PANELS!
